T1  - The Accrual Anomaly: Risk or Mispricing?
AU  - Hirshleifer, David
AU  - Hou, Kewei
AU  - Teoh, Siew Hong
Y1  - 2011/02/15
PY  - 2011
DA  - 2012/02/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.1100.1289
